{"tid":851009,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"美商務部長：未來簽訂的貿易協議或加入針對中國條款","createTime":"2018-10-06T20:18:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-06T20:18:21.000Z","uid":165683,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"fb0024c3f523faadd895ec61566b122b4a6f087f","tid":851009,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T20:18:21.000Z","msg":"美國商務部部長Wilbur Ross指，未來與其他國家簽定貿易協定時，或會加入在現時《美墨加貿易協定》中針對中國的條款。該條款是試圖堵塞漏洞的舉措，以免令對內地的知識產權和工業補貼行為合法化。若未來其中有一國與「非市場國家」簽訂貿易協議，另外兩國可於6個月內退出。<br />\n<br />\n他指，不期望在中期選舉前與中國的談判有大進展。(ic/ca)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.aastocks.com/tc/stocks/news/aafn-content/NOW.900150/popular-news\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.aastocks.com%2Ftc%2Fstocks%2Fnews%2Faafn-content%2FNOW.900150%2Fpopular-news&d=6owW%2FFrr8QAxZoJXmOkNa6S6uTmBE%2FuUnOR61Sj848o%3D&h=7b114a74\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.aastocks.com/tc/stocks/news/aafn-content/NOW.900150/popular-news</a>"}]}